1
00:00:16,620 --> 00:00:17,379
[Catch them!]

2
00:00:17,579 --> 00:00:18,899
[Protect the young master!]

3
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:24,620
[Go!]

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,620
[Black Iron Arrows!]

5
00:00:28,940 --> 00:00:29,660
[It's the Nonuple Palace!]

6
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,439
[Anyone crossing this line]

7
00:01:53,620 --> 00:01:54,739
[will be killed without mercy!]

8
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,139
So,

9
00:02:30,419 --> 00:02:32,340
it's all a lie.

10
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:34,840
Tell me the truth from eight years ago,

11
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:38,659
and I'll spare your life.

12
00:02:43,819 --> 00:02:45,719
[Even if you're not the real An Rao,]

13
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:49,000
[I don't want you to be in danger again.]

14
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,159
[Just think of me]

15
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,020
[as a killer of innocents.]

16
00:02:55,819 --> 00:02:57,159
[Let my death]

17
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,659
[be the end of all this.]

18
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,259
[Now,]

19
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,060
[I must find my beloved.]

20
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,099
[I'm sorry.]

21
00:04:40,779 --> 00:04:41,600
Who dares to break in?

22
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,279
Gu Xiang and I will cover your retreat.

23
00:04:55,180 --> 00:04:56,000
Go find your master.

24
00:04:59,779 --> 00:05:00,600
The iron arrow.

25
00:05:01,459 --> 00:05:02,360
You're from the Nonuple Palace.

26
00:05:02,779 --> 00:05:03,360
The Nonuple Palace?

27
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,019
The civilian organization

28
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,819
against the Xie family?

29
00:05:10,019 --> 00:05:10,540
Exactly.

30
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,720
Don't worry,

31
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:14,360
your master is fine.

32
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,459
The Lord asked me

33
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,759
to take you to the back yard.

34
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:19,980
After Miss Su is recovered,

35
00:05:20,259 --> 00:05:21,420
she will meet you.

36
00:06:02,699 --> 00:06:03,860
Thank you

37
00:06:04,519 --> 00:06:05,279
for helping me.

38
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:08,220
Miss Su is against the Xie family.

39
00:06:08,819 --> 00:06:09,819
We are on the same side.

40
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:10,920
You don't need to thank me.

41
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,199
The Jiu Yao Pavilion takes ill-gotten gains

42
00:06:16,939 --> 00:06:17,879
to destroy the Xie family.

43
00:06:19,139 --> 00:06:20,180
It has been heard by the people.

44
00:06:21,699 --> 00:06:22,500
Now that I've seen you,

45
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,459
I know you're extraordinary.

46
00:06:25,459 --> 00:06:27,060
I'm against the Xie family

47
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,240
for revenge,

48
00:06:30,339 --> 00:06:31,139
just like you.

49
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,560
I lost my parents when I was a child

50
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,680
and was raised by monks in a temple.

51
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:39,860
But eight years ago,

52
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,540
the Xie family killed everyone in the temple

53
00:06:42,339 --> 00:06:43,519
for a painting.

54
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,980
As long as the Nonuple Palace exists,

55
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,399
we will bring down the Xie family

56
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,720
and avenge the dead.

57
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:56,939
[So,]

58
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:58,879
[we're on the same]

59
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,339
[path of revenge.]

60
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,019
I wish you and me to fulfill our goals

61
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,899
and purify the world.

62
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,500
Miss Su,

63
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,379
since we hit it off,

64
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:15,639
and share the same goal,

65
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,660
why not bring your men

66
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,759
and join us?

67
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:23,240
We can work together

68
00:07:23,779 --> 00:07:24,899
and fight for the same cause.

69
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,600
You don't even show your face.

70
00:07:29,459 --> 00:07:30,519
I don't trust

71
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,319
such a mysterious ally.

72
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,199
Besides,

73
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:36,120
I don't like being under anyone.

74
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:37,540
Are you

75
00:07:38,660 --> 00:07:39,899
willing to

76
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:41,480
to take orders from me?

77
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:43,060
How do you know

78
00:07:44,459 --> 00:07:45,319
I wouldn't?

79
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,100
Even if you would,

80
00:07:49,259 --> 00:07:50,100
I don't need it.

81
00:07:53,939 --> 00:07:55,300
I've tamed others

82
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:57,959
to get what I want.

83
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,160
But this game...

84
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:03,980
I may not regret my moves,

85
00:08:05,779 --> 00:08:07,120
but my heart is restless.

86
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,120
Who is

87
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:13,759
the person you mentioned?

88
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,560
It's not a gentleman's behavior

89
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:20,860
to pry into others' privacy.

90
00:08:21,579 --> 00:08:22,339
Why don't you

91
00:08:23,699 --> 00:08:24,899
be honest with me first?

92
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,720
You're really agile.

93
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,100
Miss Su,

94
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,379
have a good rest.

95
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:44,799
I'll take my leave.

96
00:08:53,139 --> 00:08:54,500
Maybe I'm too tired,

97
00:08:55,379 --> 00:08:56,399
I see him in everyone.

98
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,340
Qigui, Mogui,

99
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:09,419
prepare your tools.

100
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,220
Be careful.

101
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,159
Yes.

102
00:09:11,379 --> 00:09:12,299
Shigui, Yigui, Yaogui,

103
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,480
check the passages.

104
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,440
We're safe for now,

105
00:09:17,299 --> 00:09:18,379
but we can't let our guard down.

106
00:09:19,419 --> 00:09:20,200
Don't worry.

107
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,019
I'll keep watch for you.

108
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:24,059
Let's go.

109
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,120
[Eight years.]

110
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,879
[We're this close]

111
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:36,759
[to the truth.]

112
00:09:50,139 --> 00:09:50,960
Grow up well,

113
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,419
Little One.

114
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,799
Stop patting me.

115
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,259
I'll never get any taller.

116
00:10:08,259 --> 00:10:09,340
You really are a little one.

117
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:10,620
You're so weak.

118
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:09,399
Where...

119
00:11:10,799 --> 00:11:11,720
Where am I?

120
00:11:55,659 --> 00:11:56,639
General Jin, I'm sorry.

121
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:57,799
I didn't know

122
00:11:57,879 --> 00:11:58,940
you were changing clothes here.

123
00:12:01,980 --> 00:12:02,740
You must have the wrong person.

124
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:04,320
I'm not General Jin.

125
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:05,539
No,

126
00:12:06,460 --> 00:12:07,740
it must be you.

127
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,779
Painters are good at proportions.

128
00:12:11,259 --> 00:12:12,639
I've memorized

129
00:12:12,899 --> 00:12:14,279
your height and build.

130
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:15,639
I would never mistake you.

131
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:22,840
Lady An,

132
00:12:24,299 --> 00:12:25,620
you truly are a gifted artist.

133
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,860
General,

134
00:12:31,059 --> 00:12:33,320
where are we?

135
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,980
Why do you

136
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,360
always wear a mask?

137
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:38,480
By the way,

138
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,480
have you seen my sister?

139
00:12:41,340 --> 00:12:42,200
This place is very safe.

140
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:43,320
You can rest assured.

141
00:12:43,879 --> 00:12:45,399
Your sister asked you and the Five Ghosts

142
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:46,399
to restore the painting

143
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:47,360
from the palace here.

144
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,659
There's one more thing.

145
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,080
I hope Lady An

146
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,360
won't reveal my identity

147
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,419
to your sister.

148
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,419
There are some misunderstandings

149
00:12:57,299 --> 00:12:58,019
between us.

150
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,299
I can do that,

151
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:06,960
but

152
00:13:08,419 --> 00:13:09,039
you

153
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,240
have to promise me something.

154
00:13:11,299 --> 00:13:11,659
Okay.
